PrecisAppointment of KIM STURGESS, of Calgary, Alberta, LÉONCE BEAUPRÉ, of Saint-Augustin-de-Desmaures, Quebec, AURÉA CORMIER, of Moncton, New Brunswick, and GILLES P.
